title: Kairaku no Ikenie
description:
A reprint of "Kankin Ryoujoku" with an extra chapter

1. Katei Kyoushi (Tutor)
2. Kankin Ryoujoku (Confinement Rape)
3. Byoutou (Hospital Ward)
4. Chikashitsu no Onna (Basement Woman/The Girl in the Underground Room)
5. Ningyou no Yakata (A House of Dolls)
6. Kairaku no Ikenie (Sacrifice of Pleasure)
7. Akogare no Onna (Experience Woman/The Woman I Have a Crush On)
8. Furueru Ningyou (Trembling Doll)
9. Toriko (Prisoner/Captive)
10. Yume no Naka (Inside a Dream)
